_sText:
This map origonaly started with the need for new maps in the clan Exiled gg/dm server. You can find the server at this IP: 69.90.119.135:27015

The map was drawn out by Killer, one of the leaders of the clan, and the drawn version of the map was given to me. I worked for about 2 days (total of about 23 hours) on this map. It took several compiles to get the lighting just perfect to work with the map how I needed it to. It's made so that it is a little dark, very bright in the buildings, and you can't see much of the sky. It's suppose to look like you're in a huge canyon sorta place. I thought I portrayed this canyon look fairly well. 

The map includes about 100 spawn points (although I wouldn't recomend using that many people for this map), by zones, several places to go, and well organized boxes in the inside of the buildings for strategy.

I made this map for the Exiled clan's server, but once it was done and everyone liked it, I decided I'd post it up on here. If you'd like to learn more about clan Exiled, visit our website at www.exiledclan-home.com. Or visit us in one of our many servers, you can get information about the servers at the website as well.
